Exemplary work! Truly astounding! You didn't do so bad either. Hah! I kid, of course; you've really helped us make some breakthroughs in the field of chaotic magic. If we could just figure out what the Inquest is doing in that lab, I know we could come up with a solution to the madness they created. But for now, we just need to deal with what's in front of us. Keep up the good work!

—Borpp

The humans and the charr have been at war for generations. Ascalon is now ruled by the Iron Legion—save for the fortress of Ebonhawke, where the humans make their stand. A treaty between the two could be the start of a significant peace.
